5.0 of 5 bubbles
Dragon Pearl trip on Halong Bay
Aug 2014 ‚Ä¢ Solo
After experiencing two other trips to Halong Bay, Indochina's Dragon Pearl's 2 night cruise was amazing. The cruise takes you to Bai Tu Long Bay, the outer part of Halong Bay where there is no other tourists. They have very attentive friendly staff who cater to your every need. Each meal we were served were about 8-9 courses and they catered for vegetarians/vegans. This is an exceptional cruise as it takes you to their own private island/beach and you spend time away from other tourists just being out on the water to enjoy the peace and beauty of this special place. We had a 9 course dinner in a candlelit cave, the only cruise that does this on Halong Bay. It was so beautiful and a once in a lifetime experience. I would definitely recommend this cruise to anyone who wanted something extra special. I would have been thrilled to have spent more time with them.
