Trash
Karst in the sea. Still my favorites were the ones in Guilin, China here they are not as pointy or unnatural. These are in the sea and that gives room for boat trips, which is great, if only they kept the sea in a better condition, it's painful to see.
Regarding the cruises: In my opinion all the boats are similar, go to the activities area and see the reputation of the companies there. Keep in mind that there is 3 different things involved: the agency, the cruise organizers, and the boat. Your experience and price will change depending on these 3 things.
